---
title: Minted Lamb and Feta Burger with Crunchy Spring Salad
description: A thing of such delicious, dribble-down-your-chin simplicity, the noble burger can be re-invented time and time again to create the most divine dinnertime results. For this little incarnation, we’ve taken ground lamb and thrown in a Greek twist with a minty fresh kick.
